init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee looks at you and says "I did, Your Majesty."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee looks at you with his tiny black eyes and says "No, Your Majesty.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee looks at you and says "Because you are the Queen of the Bees, Your Majesty."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The bee looks at you and says "You are the last of the royal line.
